  "items": [
    {
      "kind": "title",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "创造故事中英语现在时的 “to be” 动词",
      "file": "zh-cn-9758fb3a5734030b849148f576b765afecda468e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "介绍",
      "file": "zh-cn-b2f1469ad17de782fee6350f41c7a626f7a92005.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "大家好！今天我们来学习英语中现在时态的 “to be” 动词的三种形式。这个动词在描述身份、特征和状态时非常重要。",
      "file": "zh-cn-606495d536877ef43c90adbdda91199dc72ff005.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "在英语中，现在时态的 “to be” 动词有三种不同的形式：",
      "file": "zh-cn-b2f240216979aadd2009c251bf511b8eca32300b.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "am",
      "file": "en-us-9e56dbeff632a968c7f64f17c36f33091ce42857.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "is",
      "file": "en-us-0e9663d7d581d51c921feac4e349804643900d59.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "are",
      "file": "en-us-f7adbfc3092900b98273949b64a73d0067f5ce1a.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "这三种形式是什么",
      "file": "zh-cn-417e535d54c13766e5cddcadc5b875886ffda51a.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "在英语中，“to be” 动词的现在时态有三种用法，取决于主语。让我们逐一了解。",
      "file": "zh-cn-9dfc9685e81807d8ebcb2decf9c905b4d61257f5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "第一种形式只用于表示“我”的代词。",
      "file": "zh-cn-b0a9fb3b269e843b736f16c7d491a8c97946c1b5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "am",
      "file": "en-us-9e56dbeff632a968c7f64f17c36f33091ce42857.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "例子：",
      "file": "zh-cn-895d7bb00f5c0a5cd5cde49c758ecc844230b579.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I am happy.",
      "file": "en-us-23939b7341e0b2db15f437958c508b0842216b70.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：我很开心。",
      "file": "zh-cn-cdc6a9838439f42e5f9dfa85d6681711fb30273a.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "第二种形式用于表示“他”、“她”或“它”的代词。",
      "file": "zh-cn-006865136ea4e0f7818bd656970653e434e062d1.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "is",
      "file": "en-us-0e9663d7d581d51c921feac4e349804643900d59.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "例子：",
      "file": "zh-cn-895d7bb00f5c0a5cd5cde49c758ecc844230b579.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is tall.",
      "file": "en-us-af163ec42bea51f3309be7bba94b099b8c63c975.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：他很高。",
      "file": "zh-cn-365f9a035402d51bb5fe114937b23c41cd408db2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "She is kind.",
      "file": "en-us-019c1e9cf13b9e9edd13907ed0c10a28ab5691a6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：她很善良。",
      "file": "zh-cn-3f5c05cd933eae0050102259d2105720bd7344f8.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "It is small.",
      "file": "en-us-8f98a3230c224cbd3f93f0122c851d912157f6ab.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：它很小。",
      "file": "zh-cn-ec40868e0929f3d698f0ddf6474835a0b3720386.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "第三种形式用于表示“我们”、“你/你们”以及“他们”的代词。",
      "file": "zh-cn-fd312b4f4f91154ee7d310d32d871ce940ee863f.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "are",
      "file": "en-us-f7adbfc3092900b98273949b64a73d0067f5ce1a.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "例子：",
      "file": "zh-cn-895d7bb00f5c0a5cd5cde49c758ecc844230b579.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "We are friends.",
      "file": "en-us-f85a438612ea85b5533543e702c91062a54aebb6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：我们是朋友。",
      "file": "zh-cn-dc3bb539acb16c194748af29750c22096fdce417.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are important.",
      "file": "en-us-52a2fa8d7ca09e3d5e568b8181df5b0a2619ec73.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：你很重要。",
      "file": "zh-cn-62a20630672c788b4fbe49389869cbd4ab724b3b.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "They are strong.",
      "file": "en-us-cfdd0e2875449009f23b7ce631553918fc40c121.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：他们很强壮。",
      "file": "zh-cn-28b194829e5fbdfd163eaa7ab44c514c66ff93e2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "肯定句",
      "file": "zh-cn-fd9a2e13c91e4cfc161e2a59e738ab2fb38df183.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "在肯定句中，我们只需使用正确形式的动词来表达真实的事情。",
      "file": "zh-cn-76a28b88a8b077b42ad486482b9b83665d3f832f.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "God is good.",
      "file": "en-us-11ee17c9157ed0472cd61cd5fbf248d89b38edd3.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：上帝是美善的。",
      "file": "zh-cn-c997e1dba1e01ee71357f2e188414253aa3d8242.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "We are in the world.",
      "file": "en-us-73a7100fade0219249e864ed48cc69aabe4296cc.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：我们在世界上。",
      "file": "zh-cn-c2030216afbe2246c2ea609c00105378ae142b19.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "否定句",
      "file": "zh-cn-0e80a74d146a926afb905fd4b4635357c8074260.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "要表达否定，我们会加上表示否定的词。",
      "file": "zh-cn-0c1a66ba271411a602e40369afd03588d6df612d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "not",
      "file": "en-us-d080edbd017677fdb55d73cd176ca63f54006aa2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "例如：",
      "file": "zh-cn-dcd524d2b6d0b5ae9bd48d521b95a522716fe18a.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "It is not dark.",
      "file": "en-us-4bf230af42ce5f9aea76d38c684ccd5c930a827c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：没有黑暗。",
      "file": "zh-cn-9f9d0fe4b876dd2a38cdc3af715251660a3eed47.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "They are not alone.",
      "file": "en-us-55977a0c313b4bd0abd39c0a0ac6a29317820792.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：他们并不孤单。",
      "file": "zh-cn-71c4024570010edece3fdb26e8dfaaee83fd045e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "缩写形式",
      "file": "zh-cn-cc9ccee7f5e86762c43c59409ac2a1ac6632025d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "在英语口语中，人们常使用缩写形式，使语言更自然、快捷。",
      "file": "zh-cn-65e52ad1dac3f8345a3ae1f739d00693d5983c49.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I am = I'm",
      "file": "en-us-3551d31347d0ad0dc6f190977bd6ac041e78b193.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "例子：",
      "file": "zh-cn-895d7bb00f5c0a5cd5cde49c758ecc844230b579.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I'm happy.",
      "file": "en-us-1f6a5fb43cd019673e73d7131a98641197a01145.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：我很开心。",
      "file": "zh-cn-cdc6a9838439f42e5f9dfa85d6681711fb30273a.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is = He's",
      "file": "en-us-b273b8301973f38254d51f1afb6e01a1701abaff.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "例子：",
      "file": "zh-cn-895d7bb00f5c0a5cd5cde49c758ecc844230b579.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He's strong.",
      "file": "en-us-7cac01ef3493237e3ffd7fce80c7394626aeeeb9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：他很强壮。",
      "file": "zh-cn-5af698c150f3dadd57704b23996161d881d0d47f.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "They are = They're",
      "file": "en-us-8f94e65dda1e009000679f0c8f6a657ebd425219.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "例子：",
      "file": "zh-cn-895d7bb00f5c0a5cd5cde49c758ecc844230b579.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "They're here.",
      "file": "en-us-312f716fb2ccf7dd87290e79cb359f8381528440.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：他们在这里。",
      "file": "zh-cn-d0f1c97407235b9570c9104e577e7f77603cadab.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "这些缩写在日常生活中非常常见，使口语表达更加流畅。",
      "file": "zh-cn-0e930f690f349163e9c44ec3307f71c164636c8c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "常用表达",
      "file": "zh-cn-f8cb5877780e6a6887e11ce5f30f87bf3f106e68.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "在英语中有三个很常用的表达，可以让对话更自然。让我们来看看。",
      "file": "zh-cn-7974b2effd4cf514d2eac2c7272f5388b1cabaef.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "第一个表达可用于指出已经提到的事物。",
      "file": "zh-cn-6323b1dba121da4a7ccc9f4639e63f59a8699c00.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "That’s = That is",
      "file": "en-us-fb0028a02294b19456c93e21870aec2050934be5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "That’s God’s creation!",
      "file": "en-us-0333666b8a3d6c6e07024abe4354124f8ece8b03.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：那是上帝的创造。",
      "file": "zh-cn-efa401d64b0f298a1f49c0f1765e5e973db6ce6d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "第二个表达表示某物存在或出现。",
      "file": "zh-cn-31276e93d204db5710822b0af3d1164ad7f2d411.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "There’s = There is",
      "file": "en-us-67b470f0f332183a55d241edf38fab26cd3bba34.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "There’s light in the world now!",
      "file": "en-us-38ce9a7e80cac37ef28a68558b7ddc9f314db7b3.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：现在世界上有光。",
      "file": "zh-cn-04a1ef0ed5c4fa8d5f11baeb7e64ddb86d0d032d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "第三个表达用于指出附近的东西。",
      "file": "zh-cn-4060f9298bac99a3eb4544183836710a1f2fc3a4.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Here’s = Here is",
      "file": "en-us-d048fbe169e2253c719c31212931f30f225041dd.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Here’s the sky God made!",
      "file": "en-us-f4c87e39df9ca5070e71fc25094e4a138f71cab1.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：这是上帝创造的天空。",
      "file": "zh-cn-668f78338d3bd5c20868c87e11308381631055ce.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "创造故事中的例句",
      "file": "zh-cn-54a778f1599689ce82f106323910842ba65f3642.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "现在，让我们看看这些形式在创造故事中的例子。",
      "file": "zh-cn-1f214181f38fec3b87bbeaa4a242ea7a695a4d5c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I am Hannah. I am happy to tell you this story.",
      "file": "en-us-9542a0ba207decd1a2c01f1bd49ca878559d61e7.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：我是汉娜。我很高兴给你讲这个故事。",
      "file": "zh-cn-4c3fdce517b47a56e436b4874e2b89bf7749b8ef.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "The sky is blue. The stars are bright.",
      "file": "en-us-5e5dcdee8806b65597d4e3c244790b72a6941a51.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：天空是蓝色的，星星很明亮。",
      "file": "zh-cn-f97ab79da0e52d6bfd0423ce5c71de79ff8e8d28.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "God is the Creator. God is good.",
      "file": "en-us-9f77eeffc8a0e522ac299b9aa5a749116d8a4770.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：上帝是创造主。上帝是美善的。",
      "file": "zh-cn-85b6d1d39d43209a1b979e66581fd19320f724ec.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "That’s how the world began!",
      "file": "en-us-cdc65930162a591e3e7bf0aad7bc1c6d9c6c1e3b.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：世界就是这样开始的！",
      "file": "zh-cn-4c00b331a04e91881facb0314b5332ea63fd8a76.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "There’s a beautiful garden.",
      "file": "en-us-08dacfa2d037e475090eccc35f86ae8ec5e83471.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：有一个美丽的花园。",
      "file": "zh-cn-87c728c77fb114d384a8f2ff3faae6f4281cb7de.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Here’s the sun that shines brightly.",
      "file": "en-us-5d9143e6fbd7bb5d61cae4c165cf538b567d1408.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "意思：这就是明亮照耀的太阳。",
      "file": "zh-cn-59d761e69a0d5e80e061ff926fc94fdbce6c48bc.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "结论",
      "file": "zh-cn-477e9a11256a3d2c7320639ede60c2069c656fe6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "今天，我们学习了英语现在时态中 “to be” 的三种形式，并了解了如何在肯定句、否定句以及缩写形式中使用它们。现在，你可以使用这些形式来谈论创造世界的故事和更多内容。下节课见！",
      "file": "zh-cn-3eeafe1dd0206f602f5dbb9acc5431fd1f917107.mp3"
    }
  ]
